# HTTP requests for task management
POST  http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish the report",
  "description": "Complete the quarterly financial report",
  "priority": "High",
  "status": "Open",
  "dueDate": "2025-11-01"
}


#### Get all tasks ###
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks


### Get task by query parameter ###
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks?status=Open&priority=High


#### Update Task
PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "InProgress",
  "priority": "Medium"
}

#### Get task insights
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks/insights
